    </header>

    <main id="quote">
        
            <h2>Tailored Private Tour in Iceland: Comfort, Freedom, and Personalization</h2>
            <h3>Why Choose a Private Tour?</h3>
            <p>A private tour offers the ideal harmony between the in-depth insights of a guided experience, including Iceland’s rich culture, fascinating geology, and mythical folklore, and the absolute freedom of a self-drive trip. We've explored the advantages in our detailed blog article on the differences between a <a href="/blog/self-drive-tour-small-group-tour-private-tour/" title="see our blog article">self-drive, small group, and private tour</a>.</p>
            <p>From the moment you arrive in Iceland until your departure, we meticulously craft every element of your journey to reflect your wishes. Whether you’re envisioning a luxury adventure or a relaxed discovery, we collaborate with you to design a bespoke itinerary that matches your travel style. We offer suggestions, and you make the final call.</p>
        
            <h3>We Adapt to Your Needs and Wishes</h3>
            <p>Just below, you’ll find our form to submit a <a href="#quote" title="ask for a quote">quote request</a>. Please take a moment to fill it out in full. This ensures we can provide you with a custom-made itinerary that’s as accurate and personalized as possible from the very first draft.</p>
        
            <h3>What Makes Our Private Tours Stand Out?</h3>
            <p>We are a boutique tour operator with a team of two. Julien handles planning, sales, and guest communications, while Philippe leads operations and serves as our principal guide.</p>
            <p>This structure enables us to deliver truly individualized service. You'll work directly with Julien to create your tailor-made itinerary, and once confirmed, Philippe (who guides 90% of our tours) will be your point of contact and likely your guide. When demand peaks, we collaborate with hand-picked local guides who share our commitment to excellence.</p>
        


    
            <h2>Tell Us What Inspires You</h2>
            <p>Your journey begins with your story. Share your vision, preferences, and travel dreams using the form below, and we’ll begin curating a one-of-a-kind Icelandic adventure just for you. At Lilja Tours, we don’t just plan trips: we design custom tours that reflect who you are and how you want to explore. The more details you provide, the more refined and unforgettable your personalized itinerary will be.</p>
